  Once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a Moneky who resided on a berry tree, which was at the bank of a river. 
In the same forest , there lived a Crocodile and his wife. One day crocodile came to banks of river and rested under the tree . The kindhearted monkey offered him some fruits. The crocrocodile came back  the next day for more fruits
as he  loved them. As days  passed by, the crocodile the monkey became good friends.
one day monkey sent some fruits for crocodile's wife